Friends family and fans have gathered at the Mbombela Stadium in Nelspruit as music veteran Ray Phiri&#8217;s life is celebrated. Phiri died in a Nelspruit hospital last Tuesday after a battle with lung cancer.He will be laid to rest in Nelspruit on Sunday.Artists have taken to the stage to perform songs of worship as Ray&#8217;s family battle to hold back the tears.&#8220;It&#8217;s been a hard time. We knew it was coming but it has still been hard to accept &#8221; said family spokesperson Paul Nkanyane.Source: TMG Digital.